and its value becomes an element of the ideque.  Then a
next state function @code{g} is applied to the current state value,
and its result becomes the next state value, and we iterate.
The result of @var{f} is gathered in order, and becomes the content
of the returned ideque.
The @var{seed} argument specifies the initial state value.
