[R7RS show base]
@c MOD scheme.show.base
Formats a number with default @var{comma-rule} 3. See @code{numeric}
for details.
@example
(show #f (numeric/comma 1000)) @result{} "1,000"
(show #f (with ((comma-sep #\.)) (numeric/comma 1000))) @result{} "1.000"
