@defvar comma-sep
The character used as comma for numeric formatting, @code{#\,} by
default.
@end defvar

@defvar decimal-sep
The character to use for decimals in numeric formatting. The default
depends on @var{comma-sep}, if it's @code{#\.}, then the decimal
